Bulgaria sells 2 bln levs 12 - day discount T - bills . Bulgaria ' s Finance Ministry placed a special issue of 12 - day discount T - bills worth two billion levs and yielding 6 . 84 percent to maturity , the central bank said . In line with its usual practice the central bank did not say with which financial intitution or institutions the issue was placed on Wednesday . Details of issue follow . Price percent of par . @ Issue number BG3025597009 Type discount Term 12 days Issue date April 2 Maturity date April 14 Par value 2 bln levs Selling price 93 . 60 pct Avg yield to maturity 6 . 84 pct @ - - Sofia Newsroom , ( + + 359 - 2 ) 981 8569 
